{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/finding-a-remainder-in-javascript","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Pronalazenje Ostatka pri Deljenju u JavaScript-u","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><dfn>Operator ostatka</dfn> <code>%</code> daje ostatak pri deljenju dva broja.</p>\n<p><strong>Mfano</strong></p>\n<pre>\n5 % 2 = 1\n5 / 2 = 2 mabaki 1\n2 * 2 = 4\n5 - 4 = 1\n</pre>\n<p><strong>Upotreba</strong>\nU matematici se moze proveriti da li je broj paran ili neparan proverom ostatka pri deljenju sa <code>2</code>. Parni brojevi imaju ostatak <code>0</code>, a neparni ostatak <code>1</code>.</p>\n<pre>\n17 % 2 = 1\n48 % 2 = 0\n</pre>\n<p><strong>Napomena:</strong> <dfn>Operator ostatka</dfn> se ponekad pogresno naziva modulo operatorom. Vrlo je slican modulu, ali ne radi isto za negativne brojeve.</p>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244ae","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Postavite <code>remainder</code> na ostatak pri deljenju <code>11</code> sa <code>3</code> koristeci <dfn>operator ostatka</dfn> (<code>%</code>).</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18184,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/finding-a-remainder-in-javascript"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"const remainder = 0;","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Promenljiva <code>remainder</code> treba da bude inicijalizovana.</p>","testString":"assert(/(const|let|var)\\s+?remainder/.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"},{"text":"<p>Vrednost <code>remainder</code> treba da bude <code>2</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(remainder === 2);"},{"text":"<p>Treba da koristite <code>%</code> operator.</p>","testString":"assert(/\\s+?remainder\\s*?=\\s*?.*%.*;?/.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"finding-a-remainder-in-javascript","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/compound-assignment-with-augmented-addition","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/divide-one-decimal-by-another-with-javascript","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244ae","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/finding-a-remainder-in-javascript"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}